[20:52:35.677][VCOM] done, it either stays on the new PHY or returns to the base PHY.
[20:52:35.687][VCOM] [uint8] new PhyModeId, i.e. ID of the PHYMode we are switching to
[20:52:35.691][VCOM] [uint8] number of packets transmitted on the new PHY
