[20:52:35.707][VCOM] repeated, default is 1 if argument is absent
[20:52:35.716][VCOM] [uint32opt] delayMilliseconds before switching back to base PHY after all packets have been
[20:52:35.727][VCOM] transmitted on the new PHY, default is 0 if argument is absent. Multitimer is
[20:52:35.730][VCOM] used for delay greater than 0.
[20:52:35.740][VCOM] modeSwitchLife      Return to the base PHY after all data packets transmission for TX or after
[20:52:35.746][VCOM] MODE_SWITCH_START event and multitimer expiration after first data packet
[20:52:35.751][VCOM] reception on new phy for RX.
[20:52:35.763][VCOM] [uint8] 0=stay on new PHY (normal Wi-SUN FAN behaviour) 1=return to base PHY (special test mode)
